<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mori Calliope - HoloCure Character</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        .character-profile {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: start;
            padding: 2rem;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        .character-image {
            max-width: 300px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .character-info {
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        .stats-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .stats-table th, .stats-table td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .stats-table th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
        .weapon-section {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .weapon-image {
            max-width: 100px;
            margin-right: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

    <main>
        <h1 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">Mori Calliope</h1>

        <div class="character-profile">
            <img src="/images/calli.jpg" alt="Mori Calliope" class="character-image">
            <div class="character-info">
                <h2>Background</h2>
                <p>Mori Calliope is the Grim Reaper's first apprentice. She's a hardworking and serious individual who also happens to be an aspiring rapper. Despite her intimidating appearance, Calli has a kind heart and a dry sense of humor.</p>

                <h2>Stats</h2>
                <table class="stats-table">
                    <tr>
                        <th>Stat</th>
                        <th>Value</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>HP</td>
                        <td>100</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>ATK</td>
                        <td>1.2x</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>SPD</td>
                        <td>1.25x</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>CRT</td>
                        <td>7%</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <div class="weapon-section">
                    <h2>Weapon: Death Scythe</h2>
                    <img src="/images/weapons/death_scythe.png" alt="Death Scythe" class="weapon-image">
                    <p>Calli's primary weapon is her imposing Death Scythe. This massive weapon is capable of reaping souls and dealing devastating damage to her enemies.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Damage: Very High</li>
                        <li>Range: Long</li>
                        <li>Special Effect: Has a chance to instantly defeat weaker enemies</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

    <script type="module">
        // Your Firebase configuration and initialization code here
    </script>
</body>
</html>
